divs: sighting detailsit was around 10pm when i was at my puter reading the mufon case files on (11\15\08) and noticed two reported sightings the evening before in my area. so i went outside where there was a very bright moon which made the stars seem dim. there were scattered clouds and the air was clear. i looked around and said to myself naw, go inside its cold. i then noticed what i thought was a plane because of the different colored lights i noticed. it was far off in the distance over the oregon city, beaver creek area. from my view it was 15 to 20 degrees above the horizion. i came inside and retrieved my binoculars. to me it looked like a large star which was paulsating a very bright,clear red,white,blue light. i came back inside and called a friend of mine.i'm reporting this because someone has reported the same basic thing the following evening about 20 miles away in vancouver washington.
